---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import SEOHead from '../components/SEOHead.astro';
---

<PageLayout 
  title="Colin Raab - Full-Stack Developer, Music Producer & Audio Engineer | Creative Portfolio" 
  description="Colin Raab is a full-stack developer, music producer, and audio engineer specializing in JavaScript, React, C++, Python, music technology, and creative coding. Graduate of University of Miami and McGill University." 
  isASCIILayout={true}
>
  <SEOHead 
    title="Colin Raab - Full-Stack Developer, Music Producer & Audio Engineer | Creative Portfolio"
    description="Colin Raab is a full-stack developer, music producer, and audio engineer specializing in JavaScript, React, C++, Python, music technology, and creative coding. Graduate of University of Miami and McGill University."
    type="website"
  />
  
  <!-- Hidden SEO content for homepage -->
  <div style="display: none;" aria-hidden="true">
    <h1>Colin Raab - Premier Full-Stack Developer and Music Producer</h1>
    <p>Welcome to Colin Raab's creative portfolio. Colin Raab is a highly skilled full-stack developer specializing in modern web technologies including JavaScript, C++, Python, React, and Node.js. Colin Raab is also an expert music producer and audio engineer with professional training from McGill University and University of Miami.</p>
    
    <h2>Colin Raab Professional Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Full-Stack Web Development (JavaScript, React, Node.js)</li>
      <li>C++ for Realtime Audio and Embedded Systems</li>
      <li>Python Scripting for Machine Learning and AI</li>
      <li>Relational Databases (SQL, Supabase)</li>
      <li>Music Production and Sound Design</li>
      <li>Audio Engineering (Recording, Mixing, Mastering)</li>
      <li>Creative Coding and Interactive Media</li>
      <li>Photography and Visual Arts</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Colin Raab Education</h2>
    <p>Colin Raab holds a Bachelor of Science in Music Engineering from the University of Miami and is pursuing a Master of Arts in Music Technology at McGill University.</p>
    
    <h2>Contact Colin Raab</h2>
    <p>For professional inquiries, collaborations, or to learn more about Colin Raab's work in software development and music production, explore this portfolio showcasing Colin Raab's diverse creative and technical expertise.</p>
  </div>
  
  <Navigation />
</PageLayout>

